  "title": "In Brasília-DF, a pilot reported a large fireball falling [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/03/in-brasilia-df-a-pilot-reported-a-large-fireball-falling-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1oC",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">APRIL 26th, 1994. Time: 20:30. Duration: 10 seconds. For about 10 seconds, a commercial pilot saw, in the Plano Piloto region in Brasília, Federal District, &#8220;a very large yellow fireball&#8221;. The object was round, &#8220;very large&#8221; and &#8220;fire-colored&#8221;. The pilot informed that the unknown object had a &#8220;very fast, very sudden&#8221; speed of about &#8220;500km/h&#8221; and that &#8220;the object had a tail and when it fell it flashed&#8221;. Also according to the witness, the object &#8220;was descending sharply&#8221; at the moment when &#8220;the observer was facing the East, in the North position.&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.360. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado no Plano Piloto, Brasília, Distrito Federal</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>APRIL 26th, 1994. Time: 20:30. Duration: 10 seconds. For about 10 seconds, a commercial pilot saw, in the Plano Piloto region in Brasília, Federal District, &#8220;a very large yellow fireball&#8221;. The object was round, &#8220;very large&#8221; and &#8220;fire-colored&#8221;. The pilot informed that the unknown object had a &#8220;very fast, very sudden&#8221; speed of about &#8220;500km/h&#8221; [&hellip;]</p>\n",
